video.title: Power Rangers Time Force
video.synopsis: The team launches a new campaign against evil in the year 3000, when the imprisoned criminal mastermind Ransik is freed by his daughter.

episodes.synopsis: In the year 3000, the evil mutant fugitive Ransik escapes the custody of the elite police force known as Time Force.
episodes.title: Force from the Future: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Traveling back in time in pursuit of Ransik, the Time Force officers meet the distant ancestor of their former leader.
episodes.title: Force from the Future: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Wes weighs his privileged lifestyle against the responsibilities of joining the Power Rangers Time Force as the new Red Ranger.
episodes.title: Something to Fight For

episodes.synopsis: Ransik kidnaps Wes and takes over a television station to announce his evil plans to the world.
episodes.title: Ransik Lives

episodes.synopsis: Thirty-first century race car driver Lucas adjusts to 21st-century traffic laws as Trip develops new Vector Cycles for the Rangers.
episodes.title: A Blue Streak

episodes.synopsis: Ransik hijacks a bus full of school children and Wes's wealthy father refuses to pay the ransom, prompting Wes to reevaluate his place in the family.
episodes.title: A Parting of Ways

episodes.synopsis: Realizing Circuit is the key to the Rangers summoning their Zords, Nadira plots to capture the Rangers' robotic friend.
episodes.title: Short Circuited

episodes.synopsis: Jen struggles with her desire to avenge her fallen fiancé when Ransik releases the Fatcatfish.
episodes.title: Jen's Revenge

episodes.synopsis: A mysterious man in the future sends the Rangers a new Zord to help in the fight against Ransik's gang.
episodes.title: The Time Shadow

episodes.synopsis: Katie worries her actions in the present might be damaging the timeline and erasing events and people she cares about.
episodes.title: Future Unknown

episodes.synopsis: Lacking self-confidence, Trip decides he needs to be more like his friends and less like himself.
episodes.title: Uniquely Trip

episodes.synopsis: Wes's dad forms the Silver Guardians, a paramilitary squad to protect the rich from Ransik's gang of mutants.
episodes.title: Worlds Apart

episodes.synopsis: Silver Guardians member Eric and the Power Rangers race to gain the powers of the Quantum Morpher before Ransik.
episodes.title: The Quantum Quest

episodes.synopsis: Ransik sends a monster back to the time of the dinosaurs to steal the Quantasaurus Rex away from the Quantum Ranger.
episodes.title: Clash for Control: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: While trying to regain control over the Quantasaurus Rex, Eric tries to persuade Mr. Collins to make him the leader of the Silver Guardians.
episodes.title: Clash for Control: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Lucas protects a young girl from Ransik's gang while the Rangers try to free her kidnapped father.
episodes.title: Bodyguard in Blue

episodes.synopsis: Katie finds herself in the days of colonial Silver Hills helping a young man find the courage to confess his feelings to the woman he pines for.
episodes.title: Legend of the Clock Tower

episodes.synopsis: Jen and Wes must learn to trust in each other's abilities to rescue their friends.
episodes.title: Trust and Triumph

episodes.synopsis: Trip stands up to Ransik and Eric to protect a peaceful, repentant mutant fugitive.
episodes.title: Trip Takes a Stand

episodes.synopsis: Ransik unfreezes the mutant prisoner Conwing to steal Eric's voice so they can operate the Quantasaurus Rex.
episodes.title: Quantum Secrets

episodes.synopsis: The villainous Contemptra casts a spell of love over the male Rangers to fight each other for her affection.
episodes.title: Lovestruck Rangers

episodes.synopsis: Nadira unfreezes the criminal race car driver Dash -- a former rival of Lucas -- to help her launch a crime spree.
episodes.title: The Last Race

episodes.synopsis: Katie tries to persuade a photographer not to reveal the secret identities of the Power Rangers.
episodes.title: Full Exposure

episodes.synopsis: The heroes are trapped by Ransik's gang in various movie genre dimensions.
episodes.title: Movie Madness: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers work to escape various movie genre dimensions.
episodes.title: Movie Madness: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Ransik releases Jen's former Time Force partner to turn the Pink Ranger evil.
episodes.title: Time Force Traitor

episodes.synopsis: Frax's origin is revealed as he finally has enough of Ransik's abuse.
episodes.title: Frax's Fury

episodes.synopsis: The time travelers' actions in the present begin to change the future as a previously dead ally from the past returns.
episodes.title: Dawn of Destiny

episodes.synopsis: Wes contemplates his destiny as he weighs his duty as the Red Ranger against inheriting his father's company.
episodes.title: Fight Against Fate

episodes.synopsis: Wes refuses to acknowledge the idea of destiny and decides to choose his own path in life.
episodes.title: Destiny Defeated

episodes.synopsis: Jen and Wes go undercover to investigate a shady gym in Silver Hills.
episodes.title: Undercover Rangers

episodes.synopsis: A dark knight from the Middle Ages travels to the present with a mysterious box.
episodes.title: Beware the Knight

episodes.synopsis: The Power Rangers Time Force join forces with the Power Rangers Lightspeed Rescue to stop Vypra.
episodes.title: Time for Lightspeed

episodes.synopsis: The Power Rangers fight to escape a dimension of mirrors full of monsters.
episodes.title: Reflections of Evil

episodes.synopsis: Nadira falls in love with Lucas after reading a love poem he wrote about his car and mistakenly assuming it was written for her.
episodes.title: Nadira's Dream Date

episodes.synopsis: Circuit's memories are erased by a member of Time Force in the future, causing Circuit to doubt his ability to help the Rangers.
episodes.title: Circuit Unsure

episodes.synopsis: Ransik runs out of mutant prisoners to fight for him while Frax prepares to launch his own assault on Silver Hills.
episodes.title: A Calm Before the Storm

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers receive a chilling warning from the future as Ransik reprograms Frax and Nadira questions her life as a supervillainess.
episodes.title: The End of Time: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Wes sends the Time Force Rangers back to the future as Frax and his giant robot launch a devastating attack on Silver Hills.
episodes.title: The End of Time: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Jen and her teammates disobey orders in order to go back in time to rescue Wes and stop Ransik at any cost.
episodes.title: The End of Time: Part 3
